11:16 kai\ oi( ei)/kosi te/ssarej presbu/teroi oi( e)nw/pion tou= qeou= oi(\ ka/qhntai e)pi\ tou\j qro/nouj au)tw=n, e)/pesan e)pi\ ta\ pro/swpa au)tw=n kai\ proseku/nhsan tw=| qew=|,
