17:1 Kai\ h)=lqen ei(=j e)k tw=n e(pta\ a)gge/lwn tw=n e)xo/ntwn ta\j e(pta\ fia/laj, kai\ e)la/lhsen met' e)mou= le/gwn: deu=ro, dei/cw soi to\ kri/ma th=j po/rnhj th=j mega/lhj th=j kaqhme/nhj e)pi\ tw=n u(da/twn tw=n pollw=n,
