17:8 to\ qhri/on o(\ ei)=dej h)=n kai\ ou)k e)/stin, kai\ me/llei a)nabai/nein e)k th=j a)bu/ssou kai\ ei)j a)pw/leian u(pa/gein: kai\ qauma/sontai oi( katoikou=ntej e)pi\ th=j gh=j, w(=n ou) ge/graptai to\ o)/noma e)pi\ to\ bibli/on th=j zwh=j a)po\ katabolh=j ko/smou, blepo/ntwn to\ qhri/on o(/ti h)=n kai\ ou)k e)/stin kai\ pare/stai.
17:9 w(=de o( nou=j o( e)/xwn sofi/an. ai( e(pta\ kefalai\ e(pta\ o)/rh ei)si/n, o(/pou h( gunh\ ka/qhtai e)p' au)tw=n.
